OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772436956
OL,3,CTrump warns Iran against retaliation
OL,4,Cfor strikes which killed Ayatollah
OL,6,FDonald Trump has warned Iran against
OL,7,Ffurther retaliation for the joint US-
OL,8,FIsraeli strikes on the country which
OL,9,Fkilled Supreme Leader Ayatollah Ali
OL,10,FKhamenei, telling the country the US
OL,11,Fwould counter "with a force that has
OL,12,Fnever been seen before".
OL,14,FIn a post on Truth Social on Sunday,
OL,15,Fthe US President said: "Iran just
OL,16,Fstated that they are going to hit very
OL,17,Fhard today, harder than they have ever
OL,18,Fhit before.
OL,26,@sD@OOUtD@WO]wD@XOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
