PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772436956
OL,3,CTrump warns Iran against retaliation
OL,4,Cfor strikes which killed Ayatollah
OL,6,F"THEY BETTER NOT DO THAT, HOWEVER,
OL,7,FBECAUSE IF THEY DO, WE WILL HIT THEM
OL,8,FWITH A FORCE THAT HAS NEVER BEEN SEEN
OL,9,FBEFORE! Thank you for your attention
OL,10,Fto this matter! President DONALD J.
OL,11,FTRUMP."
OL,13,FHis post came after Iran's
OL,14,Fparamilitary Revolutionary Guard said
OL,15,Fit would launch its "most-intense
OL,16,Foffensive operation" ever in response
OL,17,Fto the deadly Saturday morning strikes.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@GO]wD@UOUxD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
