PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772436956
OL,3,CTrump warns Iran against retaliation
OL,4,Cfor strikes which killed Ayatollah
OL,6,F"The most-intense offensive operation
OL,7,Fin the history of the armed forces of
OL,8,Fthe Islamic Republic of Iran will
OL,9,Fbegin in moments, targeting (Israel)
OL,10,Fand American terrorist bases," it said
OL,11,Fin a statement.
OL,13,FIranian state TV confirmed the death
OL,14,Fof 86-year-old Khamenei early on
OL,15,FSunday.
OL,17,FMr Trump had previously claimed
OL,18,FKhamenei died in the attacks and urged
OL,19,Fthe Iranian people to seize "the
OL,20,Fsingle greatest chance ... to take
OL,21,Fback their country".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@^O]{D@]OU}D@SO]
