PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772436956
OL,3,CTrump warns Iran against retaliation
OL,4,Cfor strikes which killed Ayatollah
OL,6,FTalks between the US and Iran aimed at
OL,7,Fresolving the issue of Tehran's
OL,8,Fnuclear ambitions ended on Thursday
OL,9,Fwithout agreement, but were expected
OL,10,Fto resume at a later date.
OL,12,FFollowing the strikes, Sir Keir
OL,13,FStarmer convened the Government's
OL,14,Femergency Cobra committee on Saturday
OL,15,Fmorning, before consulting with
OL,16,FEuropean and Gulf allies.
OL,18,FLater on Saturday, Sir Keir spoke to
OL,19,FMr Trump to discuss the situation and
OL,20,Fset out the UK's role in defensive
OL,21,Foperations in the region.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772436956
OL,3,CTrump warns Iran against retaliation
OL,4,Cfor strikes which killed Ayatollah
OL,6,FIn a joint statement with the leaders
OL,7,Fof France and Germany, the Prime
OL,8,FMinister condemned Iran's retaliation
OL,9,Fand urged Tehran to "refrain from
OL,10,Findiscriminate military strikes" and
OL,11,F"seek a negotiated solution".
OL,13,FSpeaking from Downing Street, Sir Keir
OL,14,Fsaid the UK had not been involved in
OL,15,Fthe strikes, but had subsequently
OL,16,Fdeployed aircraft "as part of co-
OL,17,Fordinated regional defensive
OL,18,Foperations to protect our people, our
OL,19,Finterests and our allies".
OL,26,@qD@UOUrD@`O]sD@AOUsD@\O]xD@SOU{D@YO]
