CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772436956
OL,3,CTrump warns Iran against retaliation
OL,4,Cfor strikes which killed Ayatollah
OL,6,FHe added that protections had been
OL,7,Fstepped up for British bases in the
OL,8,FMiddle East and the Government was
OL,9,F"reaching out to UK nationals in the
OL,10,Fregion and doing everything we can to
OL,11,Fsupport them".
